description: Discover how to make a delicious chow mein packed with rainbow vegies. This easy stir-fry is ready in 25 minutes and uses frozen veg to cut down on prep time.
name: Chicken & Rainbow Veg Chow Mein Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Add stirfry vegetables and stir-fry for 3 minutes or until just tender. Add cabbage, noodles, chicken and sauce mixture to wok. Stir-fry for 3 minutes or until heated through. Top with sprouts, onion, sesame seeds and chilli. Serve.
